Canadian Finance Minister Jim 
Flaherty talks about the recent wave of businesses spinning off 
real estate assets into tax-preferred trusts.  Flaherty, speaking with Bloomberg's Theophilos Argitis on 
May 11 in Aylesbury, England, also discussed the outlook for 
Canada Mortgage & Housing Corp. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 03:41
 